  <!-- This style is overridden in the Hebrew res (iw) folder
  Fallback to system font, extra styling needed for non-latin languages
  "bold" is automatically applied to the fallback, only "medium" handling needed
  Cyrillic alphabet is supported by Jost, no extra styling needed (Russian, Ukrainian) -->
